HEADWORD: Isonomic
<hw>I`so*nom"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/;
<grk>'i`sos</grk> equal + <grk>no`mos</grk> law.]</ety> <def>The same,
or equal, in law or right; one in kind or origin; analogous;
similar.</def> <rj><au>Dana.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
